<item>
            <title>[HIVE-16803] Alter table change column comment should not try to get column stats for update</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-16803</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running command like &quot;alter table .. change ..&quot; (e.g. ALTER TABLE testtbl CHANGE col col string COMMENT &apos;change column comment&apos;&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/wink.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; to change a column&apos;s comment, Hive should not go to fetch the column stats for update since the comment change does not affect table/partition column stats.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
